title: No Man's Sky Update 4 Experimental
description:
This patch consists of No Man's Sky Experimental 4 (by machine4578).
I repacked this patch so you don't need to extract crack individually.

1) Extract everything from No.Man's.Sky.Update.4.Experimental.zip to your No Man's Sky game folder, overwrite everything;
2) Change PlayerName in file "BinariesALI213.ini"
